quran[14]{c,v,t}:
  3,130,Aey eman walo! Barha charha ker sood na khao aur Allah Taalaa say daro takay tumhen nijat milay
  3,131,Aur uss aag say daro jo kafiron kay liye tayyar ki gaee hai
  3,132,Aur Allah aur uss kay rasool ki farmanbardari kero takay tum per raham kiya jaye
  3,133,Aur apney rab ki bakshish ki taraf aur uss jannat ki taraf doro jiss ka araz aasamanon aur zamin kay barabar hai jo perhezgaron kay liye tayyar ki gaee hai
  3,134,Jo log aasani mein aur sakhti kay moqay per bhi Allah kay rastay mein kharach kertay hain gussa peenay walay aur logon say dar guzar kerney walay hain Allah Taalaa unn neko kaaron say mohabbat kerta hai
  3,135,Jab unn say koi na shaista kaam hojaye ya koi gunah ker bethen to foran Allah ka zikar aur apney gunahon kay liye istaghfaar kertay hain fil waqey Allah Taalaa kay siwa aur kaun gunahon ko baksh sakta hai? Aur woh log ba wajood ilm kay kissi buray kaam per arr nahi jatay
  3,136,Enhin kay badla unn kay rab ki taraf say maghfirat hai aur jannaten hain jin kay neechay nehren behti hain jin mein woh hamesha rahen gay inn nek kaamon kay kerney walon ka sawab kiya hi acha hai
  3,137,Tum say pehlay bhi aisay waqiyaat guzar chukay hain so zamin mein chal phir ker dekh lo kay (aasmani taleem kay) jhutlaney walon ka kiya anjam hua
  3,138,Aam logon kay liye to yeh (quran) biyan hai aur perhezgari kay liye hidayat-o-naseehat hai
  3,139,Tum na susti kero aur na ghumgeen ho tum hi ghalib raho gay agar tum eman daar ho
  3,140,Agar tum zakhmi huye ho to tumharay mukhalif log bhi to aisay hi zakhmi ho chukay hain hum inn dino ko logon kay darmiyan adaltay badaltay rehtay hain. (shikast-e-ohod) iss liye thi kay Allah Taalaa eman walon ko zahir ker dey aur tum mein say baaz ko shahdat ka darja ata farmaye Allah Taalaa zalimon say mohabbat nahi kerta
  3,141,(yeh waja bhi thi) kay Allah Taalaa eman walon ko bilkul alag kerdey aur kafiron ko mita dey
  3,142,Kiya tum yeh samajh bethay ho kay tum jannat mein chalay jao gay halankay abb tak Allah Taalaa ney yeh zahir nahi kiya kay tum mein say jihad kerney walay kaun hain aur sabar kerney walay kaun hain
  3,143,Jang say pehlay to tum shahdat ki aarzoo mein thay abb issay apni aankhon say apney samney dekh liya